{
  "info": {
    "name": "Arisan App API",
    "_postman_id": "arisan-api-collection",
    "description": "Koleksi endpoint arisan-api (BE-0 s/d BE-8 lengkap).\n\nGunakan environment 'Arisan Local'.\n\nAlur test dasar:\n1. GET /health → pastikan server jalan\n2. POST /api/auth/send-otp → kirim OTP ke WhatsApp\n3. POST /api/auth/verify-otp → isi kode OTP → {{token}} tersimpan otomatis\n4. Semua endpoint /api/* (kecuali auth) butuh Bearer {{token}}\n5. /api/cron/* dan /api/payments/cron/* butuh header X-Cron-Secret: {{cron_secret}}\n6. /admin/* butuh header X-Admin-Secret: {{admin_secret}}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:3001", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "cron_secret", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "admin_secret", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "group_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "period_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "swap_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "user_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/health", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST send-otp",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/send-otp",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "send-otp"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+628123456789\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST verify-otp",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "  if (res.user?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('user_id', res.user.id);",
                  "  console.log('Token tersimpan:', res.token.slice(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/verify-otp",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "verify-otp"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+628123456789\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
